n class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lbw1665702728801.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lbw1665702728801.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lbw1665702728801.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lbw1665702728801\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      procs\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Enable stored procedures.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lbw1665702728801__topic_d50330e1_d50331e1_d50332e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lbw1665702728801__p_d50333e1_d50334e1_d50335e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">procs</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lbw1665702728801__section_esp_qzk_3cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d137465e63\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lbw1665702728801__p_d50339e1_d50340e1_d50341e1\">This option enables the creation and use of stored\n            procedures.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lbw1665702728801__p_d50342e1_d50343e1_d50344e1\">If both the <code class=\"ph codeph\">serial insert</code> and\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">procs</code> options are enabled, the INF connector does not use the\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">insert</code> stored procedure for tables that contain Serial fields.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"lbw1665702728801__note_sqc_rzk_3cc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The connector never uses stored procedures to\n            manipulate segmented fields.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lbw1665702728801__p_d50345e1_d50346e1_d50347e1\">If this option is not present, stored procedures are\n            disabled.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lbw1665702728801__p_d50348e1_d50349e1_d50350e1\">For more information on the use of stored procedures,\n            refer to your Informix documentation.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lqj1665702728942.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>serial insert</a><p>Insert specific values into serial fields.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529486\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529486\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "procs Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 procs Enable stored procedures. USYS$INF_PARAMS procs Description This option enables the creation and use of stored procedures. If both the serial insert and procs options are enabled, the INF connector does not use the insert stored procedure for tables that contain Serial fields. Note: The connector never uses stored procedures to manipulate segmented fields. If this option is not present, stored procedures are disabled. For more information on the use of stored procedures, refer to your Informix documentation. Related Links serial insert Insert specific values into serial fields. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}